// Table
—- users
| id | name | email | password

—-- sites ---
| id | domain

--- pages ---
| id | site_id | uri

--- highlight ---
| id | user_id | page_id | location

--- comments ---
| id | user_id | commentable_id: [page_id, highlight_id] |
commentable_type | content

--- subscriptions ---
| id | user_id | source_id: [page_id, site_id] | source_type
